.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/15\/speak-evil-dead\/","url_meta":{"origin":26695,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Death: Do not speak evil about the deceased","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen your companion dies, leave him alone and do not malign him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4899 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u062a\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0627\u062d\u0650\u0628\u064f\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33355,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/sincere-dua-for-dead\/","url_meta":{"origin":26695,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Make sincere supplication for the dead","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you have prayed over your deceased, offer a sincere supplication for him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3199 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628