},{"id":43066,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/13\/salaam-living-or-dead\/","url_meta":{"origin":26695,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greeting with peace, living or dead","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Sulaym reported: I saw a man whose opinions the people took seriously. He would not say anything but that they accepted it. I said, \u201cWho is this?\u201d They said, \u201cThis is the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d I said twice, \u201cUpon you be peace,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21173,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/11\/11\/graves-desecrating-dead\/","url_meta":{"origin":26695,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Graves: Desecrating the dead like harming the living","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBreaking the bones of a dead person is like breaking them when he is alive.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3207 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_c